title: Interactive Guitar No. 39
description:
English | PDF | 246 pages | 11.6 MB





Guitar Interactive Magazine is the world's first fully interactive digital magazine for guitarists the world over. Drawing on the resources of Licklibrary - the internationally renowned music teaching resource - GI brings together expert players to analyse the styles and techniques of the world's best guitarists, which you can see and hear in the hours of video that are in every issue.
